Each field must match with the actual time to trigger a message, weekday and day of month are interpreted separatley. 1: Minutes Range 0-59 2. Hours Range 0-23, 0 is midnight 3: Day of month Range 1-31 4: Month Range 1-12 5: Weekday Range 0-6, 0 is sunday Syntax for every field: - an asterix (*) enables every possible setting of a field - single numbers seperated by commas - a partition within the allowed range (1-5) - step size within an partition of the allowed range (0-59/2: every second minute).
